Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星時請注意保持室內明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.60,0:00:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也有過心癢難熬立刻想要去做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.50,0:00:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是焦急又是煩躁的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.90,0:00:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前的表演我又感受到了舞臺上的樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.70,0:00:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想好想再次上臺表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.30,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時雅格尼斯先生要舉辦汽車展覽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的演出我也可以參加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 重點說完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力！努力！努力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也是這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的太讓人感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苗木野空真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還想再看一次……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.40,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她的合同已解除 演出也終止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.60,0:02:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有空的地方就有舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.20,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是舞臺想要把她吸引回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 關於這個他還在檢查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩•奧斯瓦爾多還是需要靜養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？雅格尼斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個好主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像總是忍不住要運動的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那天在銀行盡情表演之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要克制又無法克制似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣才象空嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰塵baba
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮亮的bibi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的bobo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也biaobiao
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝造化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把構想變為現實的時候終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開始了呢 阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 碰運氣賭一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阻止你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是人數了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起碼還需要一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連舞臺都沒有卻能感動銀行搶劫犯的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞臺上無法滿足萊恩的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪里不夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡茜小姐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓已經結束了 梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再練下去也沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是這麼想的麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算努力練習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道以後該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是想對著空說也讓我試一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失敗了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紐約見面的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過你的夢想是和我同台演出對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那時的你回答不出那之後的夢想是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.80,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也回答不出嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這次特訓就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所缺少的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是邁向舞臺所最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你所傳達出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是“請告訴我特訓的出路”的決心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.20,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要讓卡茜感到快樂的努力卻一次都沒有打動過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成為萊恩的搭檔想幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了空又想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的又是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.70,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要在舞臺上尋求的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為萊恩的搭檔、贏了空只是個過程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是這之後的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰都無法告訴你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠你自己去尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所需要的是瞭解笑容的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的重要性？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫我們來想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜她們還沒準備好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過別人都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然急促了點\N今天將召開凱納斯集團汽車展覽會出演者的甄選演出會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空也要出演的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以上臺了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 雅格尼斯先生的建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的嗎？真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所需要的是瞭解笑容的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空知道那個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼關於演出內容由美亞來給大家說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 先放命運交響曲沒什麼用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請登場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜的精彩球球小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 按照預定前進 球球們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是小組的新人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了只有今天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不加入你們的小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 很不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿娜和她的球球小組可以參加了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之只有今天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.70,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來說明那天的表演內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.10,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或許可以完成天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.00,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有……你沒有實現的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.30,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定了哦 萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定……嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確那是我唯一能為你做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰送的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特 我要出去下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去告訴她我又要上臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想瞞著她上臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請在這裏稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為見不到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雜技大賽的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我誤會你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直認為你的夢想是和我一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.70,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會以為無論什麼樣殘酷的舞臺你都能夠超越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事實並非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我無理的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.80,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至使你無法面對與梅的爭鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所夢想的不是真正的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是充滿樂趣的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所說 我所嚮往的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有爭鬥充滿樂趣的卡萊多的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我並沒有放棄成為真正的卡萊多之星的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說不和任何人起衝突還能成為真正的卡萊多之星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外我沒有第二條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.10,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免爭鬥就能達到誰都達不到的明星等級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都沒有想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.00,0:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是充滿了超乎想像的困難險阻的道路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼的困難險阻都是我自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心不再迷失方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會走蕾拉小姐指引給我的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.70,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你已經下了決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就走你自己選擇的道路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.20,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將參加這次凱納斯汽車展覽會的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓演出生動有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.20,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的眼睛中已經有了從前的神采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種熱血沸騰的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑著對我說就走你自己選擇的道路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須好好的走自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了不再讓蕾拉小姐為我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉還能看見我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 汽車展覽會什麼的應該有泳裝少女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車的主題是以自然態為主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定是要融入自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融入自然？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾物一定很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾物很少？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽的裝束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說大膽的裝束？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天演出室見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天表演時我就全盤模仿空的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剩下的路只有這條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位邊換衣服邊聽說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經去確認過舞臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子擺放位置和預定稍微有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有大的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的表演沒有彩排可能會有些緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.80,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照事先約定好的進行表演就沒有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點應對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？好像哪里不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快些去換衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是健吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.70,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然提出這樣的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能應對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中飛人小組的演出要全部更改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再考慮一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保證足夠的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.10,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團在這段時間不停的有人受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有安全網就不能表演的話根本不值得看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.70,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且攝影時拍到安全網會影響效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就做最大限度的調整吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒有考慮到實地情況是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之得想新的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原定的演出方案基本不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才這麼說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋千的位置升高了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金字塔造型的建築頂端太狹窄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.50,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全網要撤掉 又不能使用蹦床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能進行什麼炫麗的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的話離觀眾很遠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 梅 有帶著繩子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能帶著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.70,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一我帶了備用的秋千和繩索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 謝謝 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是值得信賴的男人健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼準備怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅要協助我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當……當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特 你也來表演秋千吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？秋千？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隨便做什麼決定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓洛吉特……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上 我要上場 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特還沒有正式練過空中飛人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不是很難的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我上吧 梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就照空說的做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話也是空的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.30,0:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到開演沒有多少時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 給大家說明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 空能讓這場演出順利進行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.60,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個小組就此四分五裂解散了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.70,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是基本全都要即興表演了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只要和你配合應該沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於快到空出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓空看看我的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛？一開始就是那樣的即興表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那麼我也來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.10,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即興表演的動作幅度越來越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的她我是第一次看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前她的表演完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止我都有自信贏過她的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼樣都不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天看了空的表演有種完全不同的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想贏空 雖然想贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是哪里總不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那個特別喜歡舞臺的空又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特 很棒很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 梅 開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個演技是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.10,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 空一直就在造這樣的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.80,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空擁有創造這樣的笑容的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 好帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊 梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你一直在睡覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來換花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意索菲的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜測她到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係
